plot: Jake's imagination literally runs wild, coming to life and bringing many dangers into the tree house.

In "Rainy Day Daydream", Finn and Jake find themselves stuck indoors thanks to a Knife Storm, only to find Jake's imagination literally runs wild, coming to life and bringing many dangers into the tree house. In "What Have You Done?", Princess Bubblegum tells Finn and Jake to capture the Ice King as their prisoner, but face an ethical quandary when they realize he may be innocent.—unknown
